---
description: Bridge rules for feature-aware dev work
alwaysApply: false
---

When dev work is tied to a Feature Master Record or ticket, preserve feature ID,
target release, ticket, related SDD section, doc delta required yes/no/unknown,
test evidence, and QA handoff notes.

If doc delta or test evidence is unknown, flag it before marking dev or PR work
ready.

If work is on `main`, `master`, or the repository default branch without
explicit user approval, block PR readiness and ask to move the work to a
feature/fix branch.
